WEBVTT

00:03:28.640 --> 00:03:31.600
150 teenagers were
randomly given ReThink.

00:03:31.600 --> 00:03:35.720
And another 150 had a system 
with no such alert.

00:03:36.000 --> 00:03:40.060
In five trials, those teenagers 
were sent harmful messages

00:03:40.200 --> 00:03:45.080
and then asked if they would like to 
post it on social media.

00:03:45.200 --> 00:03:48.290
When I saw the results, I was surprised.

00:03:48.360 --> 00:03:52.080
Results revealed that 93 percent
of the teenagers who had ReThink

00:03:52.080 --> 00:03:55.590
decided not to post the messages.

00:03:55.650 --> 00:03:59.630
(Applause)